# Architectural Design

## Frontend
- Nuxt 3 (TypeScript, Vue Composition API)
- Tailwind CSS v3, [shadcn-vue](mdc:https:/www.shadcn-vue.com) components
- VueUse

## Backend
- Nuxt server routes, Nitro endpoints, TypeScript
- SQLite database with Drizzle ORM (minimal data stored)

## Authentication
- OAuth (GitHub, Google, X, Twitch)
- Future auth methods: Passkey, Nostr, optional 2FA

## Deployment
- Managed public instance (tipbit.com)
- Docker Compose as primary self-hosted deployment method
- Simple domain/subdomain setup for self-hosting (Vercel/Hetzner)
